        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>1 Kings 6</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                        <l xml:id="Kings1-006-x001">Da edi dert iz seksen jylda cyqmaɣyna
                            uvullarynyn Jisraʾelnin jerinden
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            Micrinin ol dertinci jylda ajynda ijar<addSpan
                                spanTo="#Kings1-006-add001" />nyn<anchor xml:id="Kings1-006-add001"
                                type="addSpan" /> ol indelgen Ziv<ref n="1" target="#Kings1-006-fn1"
                                type="noteAnchor" /> balquvlu aj
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            oldu ol ekinci aj bij bolmaɣyna Šelomonun Jisraʾel istine da qondardy ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            ivni H-ɣa.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Kings1-006-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והבית </foreign>
                            Da ol iv ki qondardy Šelomo ol meleḫ H-ɣa altymys
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            loqot uzunluɣu anyn da egirmi loqot kenligi anyn da otuz loqot turusu
                            anyn.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Kings1-006-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והאולם </foreign>
                            Da ol ulam<ref n="2" target="#Kings1-006-fn2" type="noteAnchor" /> ki
                            oldu ol qaḥra alnynda sarajynyn ol ivnin
                            <milestone unit="page" n="107v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            egirmi loqot uzunluɣu anyn alnynda kenliginin ol ivnin on loqot byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            kenligi anyn alnynda ol ivnin.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Kings1-006-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויעש </foreign>
                            Da qyldy ivge tereʒeler acyqlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            tysqartyn da jabuqlar ickirtin.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Kings1-006-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy farsty istine
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            ol ivnin ḥuʒura civre osol farstlary istine ol ivnin civre
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            sarajɣa da devirge<ref n="3" target="#Kings1-006-fn3" type="noteAnchor"
                             /> da qyldy ḥuʒuralar civre.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Kings1-006-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">היציע </foreign>
                            Ol ḥuʒura ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            kiptegi bes loqot byla kenligi anyn da ol ortancynyn alty loqot byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            kenligi anyn da ol icincinin jedi loqot byla kenligi anyn ki kip balqalar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            bardy ivge civre tysqartyn toḥtatma alar istine stelelerin ol ḥuʒura-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            larnyn tutmasqa farstlarynda ol ivnin.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Kings1-006-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והבית </foreign>
                            Da ol iv qondarylɣa-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            nynda tigel tastan kecirgen qondaryldy da cekicler da ol balta hec temir-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            li savut esitilmedi ivde qondarylɣanynda.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Kings1-006-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פתח </foreign>
                            Esigi ol ḥuʒuranyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ol ortancy edi tarafyna ol ivnin ol on jandaɣy da qruhlyj
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            jergeler byla minerediler ol ortancyɣa da ol ortancydan ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            icincige.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Kings1-006-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy osol ol ivni da tigelledi any da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            qaplady daḥyn ol ivnin cuhurlu is byla ki edi jerge jergeden juvuzraq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            da jergelerinden erezli taḥtalarnyn.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Kings1-006-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy osol ol ḥuʒurany
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            bar ol iv istine bes loqotler turusu anyn da qaplady osol ol ivni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            ickirtin erezli taḥtalar byla.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Kings1-006-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהי </foreign>
                            Da boldu navilik sezi H-nyn Šelomoɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            ajtadoɣac.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Kings1-006-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הבית </foreign>
                            Ol iv ol uspu ki sen qondarasen eger jirisen resim-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            lerim byla da osol terelerimni qylsan da saqlasan osol bar micvalarymny
                            jirime alar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            byla da qajjam etermen osol sezimni birgene senin ki sezledim Davidge
                            atana senin.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Kings1-006-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושכנתי </foreign>
                            Da toḥtarmen ortasynda uvullarynyn Jisraʾelnin da kemismemen osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ulusumnu osol Jisraʾelni.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Kings1-006-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy Šelomo osol ivni da tigelledi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            any.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Kings1-006-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy osol farstlaryn ol ivnin ickirtin taḥtalary byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            erezlernin gruntundan ol ivnin farstlarynadejin ol stelenin qaplady aɣac
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            byla ickirtin da qaplady osol gruntun ol ivnin beroš taḥtalary byla.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Kings1-006-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da qondardy osol egirmi loqotnu qyryjlaryndan ol ivnin taḥtalary byla
                            <milestone unit="page" n="108r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            erezlernin ol grunttan ol farstlarɣadejin da qondardy anar ickirtin da birge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            qodeš ol qadašimge.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Kings1-006-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וארבעים </foreign>
                            Da qyrq loqot byla edi ol iv oldu ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            heḫal indelgen lifnaj<ref n="4" target="#Kings1-006-fn4"
                                type="noteAnchor" />.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Kings1-006-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וארז </foreign>
                            Da erez byla qaplanɣan edi ol iv ickirtin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            ojuvlamaɣy hubalarnyn da acylmaqlary ceceklernin ol barysy edi erezli
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            tas kerinmesedi.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Kings1-006-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ודביר </foreign>
                            Da devir ortasynda ol ivnin ickirtin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            hadirledi berme anda osol aron sertin H-nyn.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Kings1-006-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולפני </foreign>
                            Da alnynda ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            devirnin egirmi loqot uzunluq da egirmi loqot kenlik da egirmi loqot
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            turusu anyn da qaplady any syzɣyrylɣan altyn byla da qaplady mizbeaḥny erez
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            byla.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Kings1-006-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצף </foreign>
                            Da qaplady Šelomo osol ol ivni ickirtin syzɣyrylɣan altyn byla da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            kipledi altyn synʒyrlar byla aln⟨n⟩ynda<ref n="5"
                                target="#Kings1-006-fn5" type="noteAnchor" /> ol devirnin da qaplady
                            any altyn byla.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Kings1-006-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol bar ol ivni qaplady altyn byla tigengince bar ol iv da bar ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ⟨ol⟩ mizbeaḥny ki devirnin qaplady altyn byla.</l>
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Kings1-006-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויעש </foreign>
                            Da qyldy da berdi eki keruvim-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            ler zejtun aɣaclaryndan on loqotler turusu ol keruvnun.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Kings1-006-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וחמש </foreign>
                            Da bes loqotler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            qanaty ol bir keruvnun da bes loqotler qanaty ol ekinci keruvnun on loqot-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            ler uclaryndan qanatlarynyn da uclarynadejin qanatlarynyn.</l>
                        <l n="25" xml:id="Kings1-006-025"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועשר </foreign>
                            Da on loqot elcevi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            qanatlarynyn ol ekinci keruvnun bir elcev da bir qyjas edi ekside ol keruvim-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            lerge.</l>
                        <l n="26" xml:id="Kings1-006-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">קומת </foreign>
                            Turusu ol bir keruvnun on loqotler da alaj edi ekincide keruvnun.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                        <l n="27" xml:id="Kings1-006-027"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויתן </foreign>
                            Da berdi osol ol keruvimlerni ortasynda ol ivnin ol ickirgi da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            jajdylar osol qanatlaryn ol keruvimlernin da jetti qanaty ol birinin farstqa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            da qanaty ol keruvnun ol ekinci tijeredi farstqa ol ekinci da qanatlary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ol ortancy ortasyna ol farstnyn jeterediler qanat qanatqa.</l>
                        <l n="28" xml:id="Kings1-006-028"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצף </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            qaplady osol ol keruvimlerni altyn byla.</l>
                        <l n="29" xml:id="Kings1-006-029"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol bar farstlaryn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ol ivnin qaplady altyn byla da qursady civre ojuvlamaq byla tucurla-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            maqlaryn ojuvlamaqlarynyn keruvimlernin da ḥurmalarnyn da acylmaqlarynyn ceceklernin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            ickirtin da tysqartyn.</l>
                        <l n="30" xml:id="Kings1-006-030"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol gruntun ol ivnin qaplady altyn byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            ickirtin da tysqartyn.</l>
                        <l n="31" xml:id="Kings1-006-031"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol esigin ol devirnin qyldy esikler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            zejtun aɣaclaryndan ol isttegi odverja da ol jandaɣy odverjalar bes
                            <milestone unit="page" n="108v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            janly.</l>
                        <l n="32" xml:id="Kings1-006-032"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושתי </foreign>
                            Da eki esikler zejtun aɣaclaryndan da ojuvlady alar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            istine ojuvlamaqlaryn keruvimlernin da ḥurmalarnyn da acylmaqlarnyn ceceklernin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            da qaplady alarny altyn byla da jajratty ol keruvimler istine
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            da ol ḥurmalar istine osol ol altynny.</l>
                        <l n="33" xml:id="Kings1-006-033"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וכן </foreign>
                            Da alaj qyldy esigine
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            ol <supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>arajnyn<ref n="6"
                                target="#Kings1-006-fn6" type="noteAnchor" /> odverjalar zejtun
                            aɣaclaryndan dert janlylar.</l>
                        <l n="34" xml:id="Kings1-006-034"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושתי </foreign>
                            Da eki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            esikler beroš aɣaclaryndan eki taḥtalar ol bir esik ojuvu byla synʒyr-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            larnyn tucurulɣanlar da eki taḥtalary ol ekincide esiknin synʒyrlar byla
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            ojuvlanɣanlar.</l>
                        <l n="35" xml:id="Kings1-006-035"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וקלע </foreign>
                            Da ojuvlady keruvimler da ḥurmalar da acylmaqlaryn cecek-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            lernin da qaplady altyn byla tiz etilgen ol tucurulɣan istine.</l>
                        <l n="36" xml:id="Kings1-006-036"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבן </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            qondardy osol ol qaḥrany ol ickirgi ic jergeler capma tastan da jerge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            dertinci kesilgen erezlerden.</l>
                        <l n="37" xml:id="Kings1-006-037"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בשנה </foreign>
                            Ol dertinci jylda bunjat etildi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ivi H-nyn ajynda ijarnyn.</l>
                        <l n="38" xml:id="Kings1-006-038"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובשנה </foreign>
                            Da ol on birinci jylda ajynda ḥašvannyn oldu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            segizinci aj tigendi ol iv bar isleri sajyn da bar kecinmekleri sajyn da qondardy
                            <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Kings1006-P108v-L14" n="14"
                                next="TKow.02.004.007.xml#Kings1007-P108v-L14" />
                            any jedi jyllar.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
